title: I'm Agustin
subtitle: Here you can find information about me and you can also take a look at some projects I've made with more in progress.
about_text1:
I'm 22 years old and I live in San Clemente del Tuyú, Buenos Aires, Argentina.
I'm doing a Computer Science degree at the Atlantida Argentina University located in Mar de Ajó. I'm also in search of my first job as a Software Developer.
about_text2: I began studying by myself, taking some courses of HTML 5, CSS 3 and Javascript from the UDEMY platform. I also took React, NodeJS and Oracle SQL courses and learnt the basics of programming at University in addition to C language.
about_text3: I passed the B2 First exam (First Certificate in English) which shows that I can communicate in English fluently. In my free time, I play video games while listening to music, or sometimes I decide to make some web design projects.
typed_strings: I'm a software developer, and this is my page
